=== 12.6 Accumulating Gradients Across the Sequence

We compute the softmax-CE gradient independently at each position stem:[t].
But all positions share the same unembedding matrix stem:[W_u] (and the same transformer weights).
Their gradient contributions must be _summed_ before updating any weight.

